title: (Tues Full) Lunchbox Embarrassed Himself in front of A Country Music Icon + Why Amy’s Daughter Asked “What’s A Sugar Daddy?” + What We’d Get on Our Personalized Plates
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Lunchbox Embarrassed Himself in front of A Country Music Icon + Why Amy’s Daughter Asked “What’s A Sugar Daddy?” + What We’d Get on Our Personalized Plates
description:
Eddie says that Lunchbox embarrassed himself after not recognizing a country music icon at an industry event. Amy was perplexed when her daughter asked her the question “What’s a sugar daddy?” after she read a DM on her Instagram. Eddie saw a couple of interesting, personalized license plates yesterday so we all share what would go on ours.
